column10: Before we begin, it is very important that you ensure that you have:      	15-20 minutes available to complete this study in one go. 	maximized your browser window - whilst you are completing the ratings, it is important that you can see the items and the rating scales on one page. 	switched off your phone/email/music/anything else that you might find distracting     PLEASE DO NOT CONSUME ANY FOOD AFTER YOU CLICK the "I confirm that I am ready to begin." BUTTON.  Failure to comply with this instruction could invalidate your data and lead us to draw incorrect conclusions from this study.
